    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_010",
      "timing": {
        "start_time": 1290,
        "end_time": 1312,
        "duration": 22
      },
      "content": {
        "text": "A final choice stands between fear and release.\n\nThe door now stands slightly open.\n\nA thin line of light spills through.\n\nTHE VOICE (gentle):\nYou can unlock it.\n\nARIN grips the key tightly.\n\nARIN (softly):\nIf I open it it wont undo anything, will it?\n\nSilence.\n\nHe closes his eyes.\n\nHe turns the key.\n\nBlackout.",
